Yes Bonita is back!! The freshest  ingrediants, the real mexican recipes,  the  warmth and heart of the beautiful people that worked so hard to put bring it back into reality, this  little corner of the universe has some of the best food ever  and you all should check it out!   For those of you that never knew the food of bonita come catch this 2nd wave of it at carino, a unique and delicious mexican bistro that you will regularly visit and crave!! We are all so lucky to have these flavors back!
